"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?37/46/38633?source=related_link\">",
"      Pharmacologic management of pain during labor and delivery",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?30/37/31322?source=related_link\">",
"      Principles of labor induction",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?41/57/42903?source=related_link\">",
"      Procedure for vacuum assisted operative vaginal delivery",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
